==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: fainant
<hw>fai`n⟦eacute⟧`ant"</hw></mhw>
<pr>(f⟦asl⟧`n⟦asl⟧`⟦aum⟧N")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A do-nothing; an
idle fellow; a sluggard.</def> <rj><au>Sir W. Scott.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
